data.title: Baby Girl Name
data.meta_description: Baby Girl Name - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Aabha means glow. The document provides definitions for over 200 Indian female names beginning with letters A through B, describing their meanings which commonly relate to qualities like beauty, strength, knowledge, nature, and goddesses. Many names reference aspects of Hindu mythology or concepts like hope, faith, light, and protection.
